```{r pancreas 32206954, include=FALSE}

PMID_32206954 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32206954', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32206954 <- paste0(PMID_32206954$journal,' ', PMID_32206954$year, ' ', PMID_32206954$month,';', PMID_32206954$volume,'(', PMID_32206954$number,'):', PMID_32206954$pages)

PubMed_32206954 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32206954$eprint)

doi_32206954 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32206954$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
